    "### What are Loops?\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Loop** = A magic trick that repeats a task again and again.\n",
    "- In Python, there are mainly two types of loops:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Loop | When to use |\n",
    "|------|-------------|\n",
    "| `for` | When we know how many times to repeat |\n",
    "| `while` | Repeat as long as a condition is true |"
   ]
  },
